text: Uniharu, jasala'i pukardachan tiniharu svayam aphno palanakartakaham pahumcako madhyama khojdachan, ki tiniharumadhye kuna dherai najika huna sakdacha. Uniharu svayam usako dayako asama rahanchan, ra usako dandasita bhayabhita rahanchan? Nihsandeha timro palanakartako sajaya darnu parne kuro nai ho
